"{\"uid\": \"myjoyonline.com-botswana-declares-friday-holiday-to-celebrate-tebogos-olympic-gold-medal-success\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Audio By Carbonatix Botswana is celebrating a historic achievement as President Mokgweetsi Eric Keabetswe Masisi declared Friday afternoon a public holiday in honour of the nation's newest sporting hero, Letsile Tebogo.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 81, \"end\": 113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mokgweetsi Eric Keabetswe Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Audio\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"Carbonatix Botswana\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic achievement\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"honour\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 165}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's newest sporting hero\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo made history at the Paris 2024 Olympics by becoming the first Motswana and the first African to win a gold medal in the 200 metres.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.582055318474182e-15, \"text\": \"Motswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 241}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"the first African\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 metres\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stunned pre-games favourite, Noah Lyles, crossing the finish line at 19.46s, which was not just a national record, but also an African record in the event.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"19.46s\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"just a national record\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Office of the President issued a press release announcing the public holiday, emphasising the significance of Tebogo's achievement on the global stage.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Office\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"a press release\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the public holiday\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the significance\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo's achievement\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"the global stage\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President Masisi highlighted that Tebogo's victory is not only a monumental moment for Botswana but also for the entire African continent, deserving of national recognition and celebration.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\", \"score\": 0.9883630360302076, \"rank\": 0.011773977319648653, \"text\": \"Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\"}, {\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999783995, \"rank\": 2.1658597333272336e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo's victory\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"a monumental moment\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire African continent\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"national recognition\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"celebration\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This decision honours Letsile Tebogo as the first Motswana and the first African to win a gold medal in the 200 metres in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.582055318474182e-15, \"text\": \"Motswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"the first African\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 metres\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His performance is outstanding and worthy of the nation pausing to celebrate him in a unique, appropriate, and responsible manner that will be etched in the annals of the Republic's history,\\\" portion of the statement reads.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His performance\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique, appropriate, and responsible manner\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"the annals\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the Republic's history\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"portion\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President Masisi also expressed his immense pride and gratitude on behalf of all Batswana.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\", \"score\": 0.9883630360302076, \"rank\": 0.011773977319648653, \"text\": \"Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masisi\"}, {\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 3.0919098688359816e-13, \"text\": \"Batswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his immense pride\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"gratitude\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He commended Tebogo for his dedication and perseverance, and also extended thanks to Tebogo's late mother, acknowledging her significant role in shaping the athlete's journey.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"his dedication\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo's late mother\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"her significant role\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's journey\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Letsile Tebogo's historic victory in the men's 200 metres at the Paris 2024 Olympics was a remarkable feat.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo's historic victory\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200 metres\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"a remarkable feat\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished the race in 19.46s, setting a new African record and positioning himself fifth on the all-time world list for the event.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"19.46s\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"a new African record\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-time world list\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a thrilling final, Tebogo outpaced a strong field, including reigning 100m Olympic champion Noah Lyles and silver medalist Kenny Bednarek from the United States.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}, {\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9922564854122945, \"rank\": 0.004228006793269115, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong field\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bednarek claimed the silver with a time of 19.62 seconds, while Lyles took the bronze in 19.70 seconds, the fastest time ever recorded for a third-place finisher in the 200 metres final.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7828080511559221, \"rank\": 0.2741961537256128, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bednarek\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"19.62 seconds\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"19.70 seconds\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"a third-place\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"finisher\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 metres\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles, who had been undefeated in 26 races since the Tokyo Olympics, suffered his first loss in Paris, with Tebogo also defeating him in the semifinals.\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999936130735, \"rank\": 6.386818764224542e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{